<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2013-02-15</DATELINE><TITLE>Immunoassay Applications in Veterinary Diagnostics</TITLE><BODY>This chapter explains the technology and chemistry behind veterinary immunoassays. There is extensive coverage of infectious disease diagnosis and assessment of immune status using immunoassays for feline, canine, porcine, equine, bovine and avian applications, including the assay technology commonly used. There is also a section on the assessment of the reproductive or metabolic status of cats and dogs.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>